What is the difference between justify-content and align-items?
-justify-content controls the alignment of all the items on main axie while align-items controls the alignment of cross axis.

How do you use flexbox to completely center a div inside a flex container?
-display: flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;

Whatâ€™s the difference between justify-content: space-between and justify-content: space-around?

-space-between creates spaces between items while space arund creates space around the items from left center and right.

